    "description": "Armor Blitz is a perfect couch game with friends or go online to battle in various multiplayer modes.  Destroy other tanks, grab boosts and navigate through dozens of maps in single player or co-op campaigns; fight other players in PVP or teams mode in this game that hearkens back to the classic tank games like Combat, Triple Action, and Armor Battle.  Get fun byte-sized rushes of adrenaline as you try to defeat your enemies!<br><br><strong>Key Features:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>1 to 4 players<br></li><li>Game modes: PVP, Teams, Single Player or Co-op Campaigns<br></li><li>Over a dozen environments, like desert, forest, winter, lava to fight in<br></li><li>25+ levels in Campaign mode<br></li><li>12 Tanks, each with a main canon, and secondary weapon to annihilate your enemies.<br></li><li>In-game boosts to collect to give you an advantage, like triple shot, speed increase, etc.<br></li><li>Multiple weapons to use, like railgun, flame thrower, AOE bomb, ricochet, triple shot.</li></ul><br>Come blitz with us and have a fun, action-packed break from your daily grind...like we used to when visiting the arcade back in the classic 80s!",
